OL,3,CPrisons 'could collapse' as more than
OL,4,C2,500 prison staff could face
OL,5,Cdeportation
OL,7,FPrison unions have warned the system
OL,8,F"could collapse" as one in 25 prison
OL,9,Fservice staff face deportation under
OL,10,Fnew visa rules, ITV News can reveal.
OL,12,FConfidential government data seen by
OL,13,FITV News shows more than 2,600 prison
OL,14,Fstaff are foreign nationals working on
OL,15,Fright-to-work visas.
OL,17,FUnder Home Office rules introduced in
OL,18,FJuly, anyone earning below the new
OL,19,F#41,700 salary threshold risks
OL,20,Fdeportation when their visa expires.
