OL,3,CPrisons 'could collapse' as more than
OL,4,C2,500 prison staff could face
OL,5,Cdeportation
OL,7,FA source within His Majesty's Prison
OL,8,Fand Probation Service (HMPPS) said
OL,9,Faround 2,200 of those affected are
OL,10,Fprison officers, with the remaining
OL,11,F400 in support roles.
OL,13,FStarting salaries for prison officers
OL,14,Frange from #33,750 to #44,500 ` with
OL,15,Fonly those working the longest hours
OL,16,Finside London on the higher end.
OL,18,FThe prison service is already under
OL,19,Fstrain after a number high-profile
OL,20,Fincidents and the significant increase
OL,21,Fin the number of mistaken releases.
