OL,7,FThere have also been repeated warnings
OL,8,Fof prisons being at full capacity,
OL,9,Fyears of underfunding, and mounting
OL,10,Foperational pressure.
OL,12,FMark Fairhurst, national chair of the
OL,13,FPrison Officers' Association (POA),
OL,14,Fsaid the number of staff on right-to-
OL,15,Fwork visas is "considerably higher"
OL,16,Fthan first thought.
