OL,4,C2,500 prison staff could face
OL,5,Cdeportation
OL,7,F"The group of prison officers affected
OL,8,Fby recent visa rule changes are not
OL,9,Fjust numbers on a spreadsheet; they
OL,10,Fare becoming a core part of our
OL,11,Fworkforce, bringing vital experience
OL,12,Fand stability to our prisons," a PGA
OL,13,Fspokesperson said.
OL,15,F"Forcing these officers out in large
OL,16,Fnumbers would be a serious blow. Their
OL,17,Fdeparture will leave a gap that cannot
OL,18,Fbe easily filled ` and lack of
OL,19,Fexperience is already a key factor in
OL,20,Fwhy conditions in some prisons are
OL,21,Ffalling short.
